<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">The human readable file name, as e=
xposed to the outside. Used when sending the file for download in order to =
name the file.</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">butterflies.mp4</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>fileSize</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">int</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">File size, in bytes</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">1077923</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>mimeType</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">string</td>
