</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>uri</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">string</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>The binary file's HTTP uri. If =
the URI doesn't include a host or protocol, it applies to the request domai=
n.</p><p><strong>This attribute has been introduced in eZ Publish 5.2.</str=
ong></p><p><strong><strong>The URI is not publicly readable, and must NOT b=
e used to link to the file for download.</strong></strong>&nbsp;Use&nbsp;<c=
ode>ez_render_field</code>&nbsp;to generate a valid link to the download co=
ntroller.</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">/var/ezdemo_site/storage/original/=
application/63cd472dd7819da7b75e8e2fee507c68.<span>mp4</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>hasController</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">boolean</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span>If the media has a contro=
ller when being displayed</span></p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true</td>
