tomatically played</span></p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>loop</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">boolean</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span>If the media should be pl=
ayed in a loop</span></p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">false</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>height</code></td>
